{
  "stem": "20405.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So this was the idea of the Germans to make somebody else stronger than the other.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So, and be stronger over the other, he didn't care about if you're Jewish or not Jewish, just to save himself.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was the tricks of the Germans doing all, like this, like they did in Baron Hirsch with this Hason.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Hason was an organ of them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because Hason was taking all the-- the gold and everything and giving to the Germans, a bunch of thieves.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That's all they were-- they were doing, the Germans, just stealing from the Jewish people whatever they could.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So at the end, I forgot to tell you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Those two gold coins, where are they before?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When we were in Auschwitz, they left all the-- the clothes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We swallowed again.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And when we went to Birkenau, we got them out again.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I'll tell you what happened to those gold coins.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When in Birkenau, they put us in line, where ever, they were asking us what kind of a job was.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They say, who's a mechanic?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Who's a plumber?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Who's a-- so on.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And somebody was lifting their hand.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I'm so, I'm so, I'm so, I'm so, I'm so.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So Dario was telling me what we were going to say?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I thought saying that we are barbers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because we needed there to be barbers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They were cutting their hairs all over.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the barber always got something, bits of bread, or something else for somebody else.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Dario told me, I'm not a barber.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I don't know nothing about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Don't worry, you're going to be with me, I told him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So, who's a barber?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They say in German.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Who's a barber?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I said, me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Dario, too.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
